{"tid":1622848,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣戰線】為噴字手足提供字句","createTime":"2019-10-04T17:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T15:42:25.000Z","uid":312260,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"99340d79c4531d367ec12b219333e798bb22910b","tid":1622848,"uid":312260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:24:35.000Z","msg":"七一立會手足做咗好好嘅示範，<br />\n首先要簡單、易明同貼身，<br />\n同解釋攻擊佢嘅理由，<br />\n寫得好會係好有用嘅文宣。<br />\n<br />\n我地要將事情正名化，好似四點popo用嘅手法，另外要使用唔同階層會明白嘅句子，最好引經據典，可以提升返示威者形象之餘，仲可以免費做文宣，CCTVB都難以cut走呢啲畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n粗口唔係唔好，只係觀感唔好，已經有堆淺黃追唔到個進度，所以提出一下，希望大家都比下意見，改善下只有屌撚閪嘅狀況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港鐵</span>：<br />\n正名化<br />\n例如： 黨鐵、警鐵<br />\n<br />\n可用字句要配合目的，如果要宣傳令老人家明白<br />\n可以用：天作孽猶可違，自作孽不可活<br />\n<br />\n配合例子：721 殺人幫兇<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">政府建築物</span><br />\n正名化<br />\n例如：殺人政權、CHINAZI<br />\n<br />\n如目標係要connect國際可以用：<br />\nFree HK TIBET UYGHURS ANIT CHINAZI<br />\nWhen tyranny is a fact, revolution is our duty.<br />\n<br />\n配合例子：謀殺孩子、還眼<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔推唔陏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，大家幫幫手推post討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ee179de5069ea5426f1cfc2d0889eef23fc0ef","tid":1622848,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:24:57.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c209cf92bf9b8fdcb0c248e583d7a39a66a37cdd","tid":1622848,"uid":171838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得寫多啲英文較有影響力<br />\n好多時d鬼佬都睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b1f57e3f6b53b33cb092671f98d69b391c22c6","tid":1622848,"uid":312260,"like":0,"dislike":